title: Sesame Street Coloring Book - Fun with Friends
description:
Here are 96 images from the Sesame Street coloring & activity book "Fun with Friends." They feature the Sesame Street characters riding all manner of wheeled vehicles (bicycles, wheel chairs, scooters, roller skates), attending a carnival, petting animals, and having a picnic. The images were scanned at 150-dpi. They are black-and-white and can easily be reprinted on 8.5 x 11 pages for rainy days at home.
